task.summary: Basic support for handling keyboard input has been added to Console and implemented in IOModes.

Added character list to Gamestate.
Implemented basic engine loop.
Updated modes to start and stop engine.

Added MenuMode and MainMenuMode.
Updates to Console to provide information necessary to support MenuModes.
Fixed a font size bug in Renderer.

Bugfix: Clear the engine instance when the thread terminates.
Fixed a typo in Main Menu placeholder text.
Refactored /items Consolidated offense & defense stats into single stat variable

Basic implementation of actions and engine loop.
Implementation of player movement controls.
ConsoleInterface.drawFloor() now correctly uses actor locations rather than a hack to draw characters.

1. Bigroom6(), Deans office, Dept. chair, assistant 2. Rooftop(), roof top, greenhouse
Added 2 rooms.

Player Inventory is now an ArrayList<Item>, not an Item[].
Simplified addToInventory and removeItemFromInventory to make use of ArrayList API.
Updated Test_PlayerCharacter to assert Inventory.size() = 0(rather than that each index is null).

Added a message for player level up.
Added color to information panels.
Added information panel for player stats.
